  "identifier": "SJR 18",
  "title": "DESIGNATING AUGUST 31, 2026, AS \"INTERNATIONAL OVERDOSE AWARENESS DAY\" IN THE STATE OF DELAWARE AND REQUIRING THE STATE FLAG TO BE FLOWN AT HALF-STAFF IN OBSERVANCE.",
  "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}",
